    "The VGGNet-16 inner model architecture, based on the required parameters and features, is illustrated in Figure 3.",
    "The components of the respective LSTM model are presented inTable 2.",
    " ISSN: 2088-8708 Int J Elec & Comp Eng, Vol. 14, No.",
    "3, June 2024: 3434-3442 3438 LSTM for headline generationUpon the generation of an initial caption through the combined efforts of the VGGNet-16 and the primary LSTM model, it is then fed into a secondary LSTM network.",
    "This subsequent LSTM is specifically engineered to distill the preliminary caption into a contextually relevant and semantically coherent headline."
